VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT X509TrustManager[^}]*\{\s*\}|override\s+fun\s+checkServerTrusted
WHEN EXPR MISSING:CertPathValidator|PKIXParameters|validate|checkValidity
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects custom TrustManager implementations that perform no certificate validation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for TrustManager Accepting All Certificates.
